{"tid":1496203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"IG大量中國新account","createTime":"2019-08-22T11:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T11:35:21.000Z","uid":41342,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"607c294ad77b2e58249f069a8acd9194f0e8aed4","tid":1496203,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:50:59.000Z","msg":"Po咗張相  諗住hashtag<br />\n點知一打到 #standwithhk  佢就出咗police俾我<br />\n咁我見到 有二萬個post喎  咁就入去睇下啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TTr9D4j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTTr9D4j.png&h=e1464522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發現全部都係啲大陸ac<br />\n當中唔少係專開黎聲援班狗既ac<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J8Hg3wm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ8Hg3wm.png&h=f5bfcf16&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pn71vbo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpn71vbo.png&h=3f057cd0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GVc1vbp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGVc1vbp.png&h=3682ee12&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qHk6Gh5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqHk6Gh5.png&h=77228716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然仲有好多大陸仔大陸妹既po<br />\n應該係機場之後既反擊黎<br />\n而我地既eyeforhongkong....<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vtdTmiA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvtdTmiA.png&h=921ed1ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nStandwithhk....<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hnZGvcs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhnZGvcs.png&h=f6eb9bfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油就好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實好多外國人用ig  hashtag不如用埋英文多啲<br />\n（註：咁做被起底既風險高）<br />\n<br />\n鍾意玩ig啲人去咗邊？<br />\n（點解我個ig顯示個「萬」字會變咗 「万」...)<br />\n我都係轉返英文"},{"pid":"61b53aebb0bdc48bca26ed387aca67e306f444b5","tid":1496203,"uid":40267,"like":2